James Gregoire was killed following 'altercation' in Clacton town centre last night  . 
  Police have arrested a 21-year-old man on suspicion of murder in connection with the death . 
  The victim was known locally as 'Pongo' and was found dead in an alleyway . 
  A second man was seriously injured in the brawl . 
  Essex Police have closed off a large area of the town centre . 
 